import React from 'react';
import {Box, Typography} from '@mui/material'

export default function Home() {
    return (
      <Box sx={{p: 5, m: 5}}>
          <Box sx={{mb: 3}}>
              <Typography variant="h2">
                  Welcome to LotoMania: Your Gateway to Excitement and Fortune!

                  lottery games.

          </Box>
          <Box sx={{mb: 3}}>
